---
import BlockOffLayout from '../../layouts/BlockOffLayout.astro';
---

<BlockOffLayout
  title="Support | Block OFF"
  description="Get support for Block OFF early access, YouTube moderation, Instagram moderation, account setup, and comment review workflows."
  canonicalPath="/blockoff/support"
>
  <header class="site-header page-header">
    <a class="brand" href="/blockoff" aria-label="Block OFF home"><img src="/blockoff/block-off-logo.png" alt="" /><span>Block OFF</span></a>
    <nav class="main-nav" aria-label="Primary navigation"><a href="/blockoff/#product">Product</a><a href="/blockoff/#how">How it works</a><a href="/blockoff/#dashboard">Dashboard</a><a href="/blockoff/#pricing">Pricing</a></nav>
    <a class="header-cta" href="/blockoff/#pricing">Try now</a>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero"><span class="section-kicker">Support</span><h1>Help for early users and founding creators.</h1><p>Block OFF is pre-launch. This support page explains the expected setup path and where to ask for help.</p></section>
    <section class="legal-layout">
      <nav class="legal-nav" aria-label="Support sections"><a href="#setup">Setup</a><a href="#youtube">YouTube</a><a href="#instagram">Instagram</a><a href="#billing">Launch offer</a></nav>
      <div class="support-grid">
        <article class="support-card" id="setup"><h2>Getting started</h2><p>Join the waitlist, claim the launch offer when payments open, then connect a supported YouTube or Instagram profile during onboarding.</p></article>
        <article class="support-card" id="youtube"><h2>YouTube moderation</h2><p>The MVP will focus on scanning new comments, applying rules, hiding risky comments, and showing activity in the review dashboard.</p></article>
        <article class="support-card" id="instagram"><h2>Instagram moderation</h2><p>Instagram support is planned for eligible creator or business accounts where platform permissions allow comment moderation workflows.</p></article>
        <article class="support-card" id="billing"><h2>Launch offer</h2><p>The founding offer is designed as three months for the price of one month. Payment and access instructions will be sent to early users.</p></article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <a class="brand footer-brand" href="/blockoff" aria-label="Block OFF home"><img src="/blockoff/block-off-logo.png" alt="" /><span>Block OFF</span></a>
    <nav aria-label="Footer navigation"><a href="/blockoff/privacy">Privacy Policy</a><a href="/blockoff/terms">Terms & Conditions</a><a href="/blockoff/returns">Returns & Refunds</a><a href="/blockoff/about">About Us</a><a href="/blockoff/contact">Contact Us</a><a href="/blockoff/support">Support</a><a href="/blockoff/changelog">Changelog</a></nav>
  </footer>
</BlockOffLayout>
